cast.overview: Dangal is an extraordinary true story based on the life of Mahavir Singh and his two daughters, Geeta and Babita Phogat. The film traces the inspirational journey of a father who trains his daughters to become world class wrestlers.
cast.title: Dangal

details.biography: Fatima Sana Shaikh is an Indian actress and also a photographer. She appears in Bollywood movies and television serials. She started her film carrer with the 1997 film Chachi 420 in which she plays the role of Bharti, Jai and Janki Paswan's daughter. In her most recent role, she plays Geeta Phogat, an Indian wrestler and Mahavir Singh Phogat's daughter in the Bollywood film Dangal.
details.name: Fatima Sana Shaikh
